item.title: CVE-2020-10750|2024-08-04T11:14:15.575Z -- the%20jager%20project -- jaegertracing%2Fjaeger
item.description: Sensitive information written to a log file vulnerability was found in jaegertracing/jaeger before version 1.18.1 when the Kafka data store is used. This flaw allows an attacker with access to the container's log file to discover the Kafka credentials.
